bioLockJ

Class Constants

  • java.lang.Object
    • bioLockJ.Constants
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BioLockJ, ConfigUtil

    public abstract class Constants
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the root class for BioLockJ containing all constant values. The purpose of this class is to improve readability of code within it's subcalsses.
